ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectAgri-Recovery - 2011 Canada-British Columbia Excess Moisture Initiative
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide assistance through the Agricultural Disaster Relief Program under the federal-provincial-territorial AgriRecovery Framework, in order to help vegetable producers from BRITISH COLUMBIA address the impacts of the excessive moisture received in 2010 and the prolonged effects it is having on the seeding of the 2011 crop.
